        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img loading="lazy" class="Badges img_ev3q" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/author-yuanyp8-yellowgreen"><br><br><p>awk 配置 prinf 实现批量执行命令</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_WYt5" id="awk-简介">awk 简介<a class="hash-link" href="#awk-简介" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><p>awk 是一种编程语言，用于在linux/unix下对文本和数据进行处理。数据可以来自标准输入(stdin)、一个或多个文件，或其它命令的输出。它支持用户自定义函数和动态正则表达式等先进功能，是linux/unix下的一个强大编程工具。它在命令行中使用，但更多是作为脚本来使用。awk有很多内建的功能，比如数组、函数等，这是它和C语言的相同之处，灵活性是awk最大的优势。</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_WYt5" id="命令行格式">命令行格式<a class="hash-link" href="#命令行格式" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">awk: option requires an argument -- h</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">Usage: </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">awk</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">POSIX or GNU style options</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> -f progfile </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">--</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">file</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">..</span><span class="token plain">.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">Usage: </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">awk</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">POSIX or GNU style options</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">--</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'program'</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">file</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">..</span><span class="token plain">.</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><details class="details_lb9f alert alert--info details_b_Ee" data-collapsed="true"><summary>参数</summary><div><div class="collapsibleContent_i85q"><div><div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        -f progfile             --file</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain">progfile</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34